/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a serene scene of a tree-lined street in Beijing, China. The trees, stripped of their leaves, stand tall on either side of the street, their bare branches reaching out to the clear blue sky above. The perspective of the image is from ground level, looking down the length of the street, giving a sense of depth and continuity. The street itself is devoid of any traffic or pedestrians, adding to the tranquility of the scene. In the distance, a few buildings can be seen, their muted colors blending harmoniously with the natural surroundings. The overall color palette of the image is dominated by shades of green from the trees, brown from the earth, and blue from the sky.
